name: INPlayMediaMediaItemUnsupportedReason
desc: Reasons the app can’t play the media item.

items.name: case loginRequired
items.desc: The user must log in to the app.

items.name: case subscriptionRequired
items.desc: The user must have a subscription to the app's service.

items.name: case unsupportedMediaType
items.desc: The media's type is not supported.

items.name: case explicitContentSettings
items.desc: The content settings don’t allow the user to play the media item.

items.name: case cellularDataSettings
items.desc: The cellular data settings don’t allow the user to play the media item.

items.name: case restrictedContent
items.desc: The media item is restricted content.

items.name: case regionRestriction
items.desc: The media isn’t available in the user’s geographic location.

items.name: case serviceUnavailable
items.desc: The app can’t add the item because its media service isn’t available.
